{
  "text": "All interviews and focus groups took place in the ward or clinic environment in which the staff worked to enhance the sense of control and ease among participants [CITATION_1] . Interviews were conducted by the first author, who although not trained in focus group facilitation, had training in conducting therapeutic and psychoeducational groups.",
